Twenty mg of each microcapsule was added to 2 mL of a methanol and ethanol solution at a 1:1 ratio for 2 min. Each mixture was filtered after two minutes under a vortex35. The Folin-Ciocalteu reagent was used to measure each SPC microcapsule filtrate as previously mentioned. Equation 2 was used to determine the EE of the prepared microcapsules:2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
